videos.description: Jared Harper blows by the defender and finds Austin Wiley for the alley-oop jam.
videos.headline: Wiley throws down dunk off assist from Jared Harper

videos.description: Markell Johnson gets in the paint and drops the perfect no-look pass to Wyatt Walker who throws it down with two hands.
videos.headline: Johnson makes sweet no-look pass to Walker for dunk

videos.description: NC State guard Markell Johnson gets the hand-off pass and knocks down the 3-pointer plus the foul.
videos.headline: NC State's Johnson drains the 3 while fouled

videos.description: Markell Johnson gets the steal and tries the dunk but blows a tire and ends up making the layup.
videos.headline: Johnson gets steal and layup extending NC State's lead
